OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 14 MAY
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1976FPeter Woods was taken off air as
OL,7,Fhe read the opening headlines on
OL,8,FNewsday (BBC Two).
OL,9,
OL,10,FViewers complained that Woods appeared
OL,11,Fto be drunk, as his speech was slurred.
OL,12,FThe official line from the BBC was that
OL,13,Fhe had suffered a reaction to
OL,14,Fmedication.
OL,15,
OL,16,FHe was sent home and replaced as
OL,17,Fpresenter of Newsnight later that
OL,18,Fevening on BBC Two.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG2005FJohn Inverdale presents Rugby
OL,21,FSpecial (BBC Two) for the final time.
OL,22,
